      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHARGE THE CARD (3) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth (20.28) in a Grade 5 at this track. Form here sound including three wins. Can bounce back. ZIPPING LARGO (8) has missed the frame at her last couple but wasn't beaten far three back when second (19.75) at this track in a Grade 5. Has the ability and can find best this time. BOGAN WHISKEY (1) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 4.5 lengths at this track in a handy 19.89 beating Midnight Hazard. The form out of his last race has been franked. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. GREYSYND QUINN (6) gave nothing else a chance most recently. Must be respected.",
